com.mathgame.offline

Class TypeManagerO

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mathgame.offline.TypeManagerO

  • public class TypeManagerO
extends java.lang.Object
    The TypeManagerO class handles the different types of games and converts between values of different types. It is designed for offline play (unlike the TypeManager class), and it does not contain it's own MathGame object
